	heroSubhead={`You have walked an honest road — facing suffering clearly, practicing compassion, seeking peace through stillness and discipline. Here is a gentle invitation: there is a personal Father who meets you in the very suffering you have faced so bravely, who loves you, and who offers you rest — so you do not have to carry the path alone.`}
