		{ ref: `John 14:27`, slug: `john`, ch: 14, text: `Peace I leave with you; My own peace I give to you. I do not give as the world gives. So do not let your heart be troubled or afraid.`, note: `A peace that is given, not earned — received as a gift rather than achieved through striving.` },
