		{ ref: `Psalm 34:18`, slug: `psalms`, ch: 34, text: `The Father is near to the brokenhearted, and He saves those who are crushed in spirit.`, note: `He does not stand far off from suffering. He draws near to the very ones in pain.` },
		{ ref: `Isaiah 41:10`, slug: `isaiah`, ch: 41, text: `Do not be afraid, for I am with you; do not be dismayed, for I am your Father. I will strengthen you and help you; I will hold you with My right hand.`, note: `You are not walking the path alone. A Father is with you, holding you through it.` },
		{ ref: `Matthew 6:26`, slug: `matthew`, ch: 6, text: `Look at the birds of the sky; they do not sow or reap or store away, yet your heavenly Father feeds them. Are you not much more precious to Him?`, note: `The Father's care does not have to be earned by effort. He provides freely, because you are precious to Him.` },
