		{ question: `What makes the Father's Heart Bible™ different?`, answer: `It's the first English translation to reveal God as Father wherever Scripture reveals Him as Father. For someone who has walked a path of seeking peace through their own effort, that reframes the whole story: you are not a lone seeker laboring toward enlightenment, but a beloved child welcomed by a Father who comes near in your suffering and offers rest. Read it free at fathersheartbible.com/read.` },
